Dil Se..;;1998;;Not Rated;;Drama,Romance;;7.6;;Mani Ratnam;;Shah Rukh Khan,Manisha Koirala,Preity Zinta,Raghuvir Yadav,Sabyasachi Chakrabarty,Piyush Mishra,Krishnakant,Aditya Srivastav,Ken Philip,Sanjay Mishra,Mita Vashisht,Arundhati Rao,Malaika Arora,Gautam Bora,Manjit Bawa,Zohra Sehgal,B.M. Shah,Gajraj Rao;;Amar Varma, a producer for Indian news radio, meets an enigmatic woman at a railroad station and then again at a hill station. He falls in love with her, but the woman, who calls herself Meghna, rejects and leaves him although she seems to be interested. Later, Varma agrees to marry his family's choice, Preeti. But suddenly Meghna is back, and what is the secret that she holds?;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0164538/